               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1472" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1472" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1472" type="surname" value="NEWPORT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1472" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>BENJAMIN NEWPORT</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at the corner of North-street, East India-road, and am a carpenter. I have a shed in my garden, and lost a pair of</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184306120212"></xptr>
               <p>small truck wheels from it—I saw them again, on the 9th of June, at Mr. Mat<lb></lb>thews's—I am sure they are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1473" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1473" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1473" type="surname" value="MATTHEWS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1473" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM MATTHEWS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a broker, and live in Salmon's-lane. On the 15th of April the prisoner brought me this pair of wheels—he said his truck was run over and broken, and he could not sell his articles—I bought the wheels of him for half-a-crown—I am sure he is the man.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1474" type="witnessName">
